hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: I'm not working at the moment pharmatraining Her grandchildren, Matilda, 13; Cosmo, 11; Jemima, nine and Lila, four, would certainly not be allowed to do anything like that, nor do they have servants to contend with – though nowadays there are staff running the public areas of the house. Burghley is infinitely more organised these days (“Boring,” laughs Lady Victoria) but there are still hidden corners – and even adults get surprises.
